Summary
											
												On October 30, 2015, Pinellas County Law Enforcement arrested 63-year-old John Stephen Holmes for DUI in Pinellas, Florida. He is 508 tall, weighs 160 and has brown eyes. DUI is a MISDEMEANOR offense but all suspects are presumed innocent until proven guilty. Information about upcoming court dates for Holmes may be obtained from one of the following law enforcement or prosecuting agencies: Pinellas County Law Enforcement.											




 







